data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and potential in this charming 3-bedroom ranch. Step inside to find a bright and open floor plan that welcomes you with abundant natural light. The spacious living area seamlessly flows into a well-appointed kitchen, creating an ideal space for daily living and entertaining.The lower level features a single-car garage and  a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. Envision a family room, home office, gym, or guest suite - the possibilities are endless. Plus, the walk-out design provides easy access to the great yard-ideal for outdoor activities .This home is perfectly situated in the Chartiers Houston school district. Additionally, you'll have quick access to major highways, including I-79 and I-70, ensuring a convenient commute. Southpointe, known for its corporate offices and amenities, is just around the corner. There are a  wide array of entertainment, dining, and shopping options.
